# 📖 StoryWeave – AI-Powered Story Generator

StoryWeave is an AI-based website that helps users generate creative stories based on their prompts. Built using Flask and Together AI, this project brings storytelling to life!

🚀 Features
- AI-powered story generation
- Simple and interactive UI
- Powered by Flask & JavaScript
- Deployed for online access

🛠 Tech Stack
- **Frontend:** HTML, CSS, JavaScript  
- **Backend:** Flask (Python)  
- **AI Model:** Together AI API  

⚙️ Installation
1️⃣ Clone the repository
```sh
git clone https://github.com/Eunice-Joshi/StoryWeave.git

Website:
https://storyweave-lac.vercel.app/
